Package: qmc2-sdlmame
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, qmc2-data, qmc2-runonce, libqtgui4 (>= 4.8.0), libphonon4, libqtwebkit4, libqt4-test, libqt4-sql-sqlite, sdlmame (>= 0.162) | mame (>= 0.162)
Replaces: qmc2 (<= 0.34), qmc2-sdlmess (<= 0.51), qmc2-sdlume (<= 0.51)
Description: M.A.M.E. Catalog / Launcher II
 QMC2 is a Qt 4 based multi-platform GUI front end for several MAME, MESS and
 UME variants. This package provides the MAME variant of QMC2.

